tr.th: Conclusion and Recommendations based on this report and previous findings known to us

tr.td: All measured parameters are within normal limits except for a mildly decreased HbA1c, which may reflect recent changes in glucose metabolism, possible anemia, or laboratory variation. Renal function, electrolytes, and glucose are normal. No acute laboratory abnormalities detected; clinical correlation is recommended.
